:

1. *Danas* je petak. (Today is Friday.)
2. *Dan* je bio sunčan. (The day was sunny.)
3. Ona je svakog *dana* u školi. (She is at school every day.)
4. Učio je celu *noć*. (He studied all night.)
5. *Danima* smo se spremali za put. (We have been preparing for the trip for days.)
6. *Današnji* sastanak je odložen. (Today's meeting is postponed.)